     H            Y.
     F** UEXR29A ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: CHECK EDI CUSTOMER OR NOT                 *
     F*
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2023.08.23                       *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR29A'
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*  IN  $NONY :  4A DELIVERY#
     F*  OUT $RTN  :  1A RETURN CODE (Y:YES, N:NO)
     F******************************************************
     FAB#PL1Q2IF  E           K        DISK
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      * CHECK NONY=0
     C           @NONY     IFEQ 0000
     C           @NONY     OREQ 9999
     C                     GOTO ENDP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * CHECK PP100
     C           @NONY     CHAINAB#PL1Q2             98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVEL'Y'       $RTN
     C                     GOTO ENDP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           ENDP      TAG
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *======================================================
      * INITIAL SET
      *======================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      * SET KEY
     C           $NONY     IFEQ ' '
     C                     Z-ADD0         @NONY   40
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     @NONY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVEL'N'       $RTN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
